page.title: 16Services, Stetchworth area
page.content: For{Local Government}purposes the area comes within the East Cambridgeshire District of Cambridgeshire County Council. All of the area has mains water and electricty but mains gas is not available. The water tower which supplies the area is at Woodditton. The local Telephone exchange is { {Stetchworth}but the building housing } it is at Dullingham. The nearest{Doctor}is at the Health Centre in The Rookery, Newmarket. Telephone Newmarket The nearest {Hospital}with an accident department is Addenbrookes Hospital, Cambridge. The {Police }House for the area is at High Street, Stetchworth. Telephone
